kquote><br />\n你睇下味千係港交所既報告其實就知味千既由來<br />\n味千係熊本係間好撚廢既拉麵<br />\n有日有個大陸婆商人去日本撞到味千老細，就同佢講&quot;ohaiyo! wanna make some money at China?&quot;<br />\n然後兩條友合作透過瘋狂宣傳將味千包裝成正宗日本拉麵<br />\n日本人一睇就知係on9，但大陸人同香港人就被呢d包裝呃到成隻狗咁，成日以為味千好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff16bfcf115fc806ab20a2e4a79e398e4c77bcf","tid":200473,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:03:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話味千係大陸野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來都係始於日本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前去過熊本食味千對家<br />\n隻味一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n味千根本係搬番日本隻味黎香港<br />\n<br />\n利申：對上一次食味千係10年前</blockquote><br />\n你睇下味千係港交所既報告其實就知味千既由來<br />\n味千係熊本係間好撚廢既拉麵<br />\n有日有個大陸婆商人去日本撞到味千老細，就同佢講&quot;ohaiyo! wanna make some money at China?&quot;<br />\n然後兩條友合作透過瘋狂宣傳將味千包裝成正宗日本拉麵<br />\n日本人一睇就知係on9，但大陸人同香港人就被呢d包裝呃到成隻狗咁，成日以為味千好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nd麵勁撚少,芽菜就多囉<br />\n又唔係好味...差唔多10年冇食過"},{"pid":"d3224820c1e49e456daa66be81354f2cdb714468","tid":200473,"uid":7424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:05:04.000Z","msg":"咁撚難食都入圍<br />\nD煲仔飯可以拎去餵狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83caef60c3d86bad457e33968404b8c817cb4556","tid":200473,"uid":17427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:06:22.000Z","msg":"邊撚個最喜愛呢兩間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1748715cdc030caf91c255a603bbebfad26618d9","tid":200473,"uid":2211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"又係大家樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e012f342b2ad112f1bf2790518cf386cecd79301","tid":200473,"uid":15339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r